    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="letter">
                <div type="text">
                    <opener>
                        <placeName>Bayswater</placeName>
                        <date>January 17th 1839</date>
                        <salute>My dear Sir,</salute>
                    </opener>
                    <div type="transcription">

                  <p>I am delighted to think that you have finished the Review, and more obliged to you than I can express, for having done so. If you will send it to me, to the care of Messrs Longmans, I will have a copy of it taken, lest it should be lost, and then send the original to Mr Black, and ask him to take it, and deliver with his own hands (which he will do, being an old Schoolfellow, and particular friend of mine</p>
                  <p>J. S. Henslow Esq.</p>
                        
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </body>
